hypermedia:
- look in the document for urls
- github uses a *_url convention
- atompub uses <link rel="" href="">
- present all links as a TOC
- parse differences and present humanized as collections/resources

resource view:
- all non hypermedia is displayed in a table
- binary data
- regular data
- links
- coordinates
- dates
